&lt;li&gt;A genuine curiosity regarding the digital assets sector and institutional financial markets and an interest in portfolio, execution or order management systems.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Passionate about software engineering and about delivering a quality product&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborative spirit with an enthusiasm for taking ownership of tasks and professional development.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborative, enthusiastic, and excellent communication skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
